<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">

    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff7fb 0%, #fffdf9 100%);
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .success-wrap {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0 16px;
        }

        .success-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.96);
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 35px rgba(210,170,188,0.18);
            padding: 36px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .title {
            color: #7f5b71;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .order-id {
            color: #5f7898;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .btn-home {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffb6c9, #ffc9a9);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../navbar.ejs') %>

    <div class="success-wrap">
        <div class="success-card">
            <div class="icon">🎉</div>
            <h2 class="title">สั่งซื้อสำเร็จแล้ว</h2>
            <div class="order-id">เลขออเดอร์: <%= orderId %></div>
            <p>ระบบได้บันทึกคำสั่งซื้อและรายการขายเรียบร้อยแล้ว</p>
            <a href="/sales/all" class="btn-home">ดูรายการขาย</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>